title: [FSX/P3D] Milviz Northrop T-38A Talon v3.140428
description:
Time for a little upgrade!

Brought to you guys here at TPB by me, and possibly for the first time over the internet, here is Milviz T-38A Talon v3.140428 for you!

This upload contains both FSX and P3D V2 versions of this aircraft. The FSX version can also be used in P3D v1.x.

This is currently the latest version of this aircraft.

READ the Readme file I prepared for you BEFORE installing this.

Enjoy!
